{"tid":1988761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"禁聚令推行近1個月　檢控1娛樂場所52食肆","createTime":"2020-04-25T12:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T12:05:58.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af8ae4b8858d43adaae363113c08a32647af8f96","tid":1988761,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T12:05:58.000Z","msg":"政府自上月28日實施禁聚令及停業令，嚴禁4人以上聚集，限制食肆最多4人一枱，並關閉健身室、酒吧、美容院等高風險場所，截至今日(25日)凌晨，警方、食物環境衞生署、康樂及文化事務署及衞生署等6個部門，共巡查8,944次遊戲機中心、健身中心、美容院等11類要暫停營業的「表列處所」，共發出60宗勸喻，僅有1宗檢控。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200425/bkn-20200425162727050-0425_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200425%2Fbkn-20200425162727050-0425_00822_001.html&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=3f63b21f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200425/bkn-20200425162727050-0425_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n恐懼撚: 支持政府嚴正執法!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;抗疫要緊!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}